{"tid":2426582,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★上海一名 iPhone 用戶不滿 iOS 內購比 Android 貴，要求賠償 10 萬人民幣，獲法院受理","createTime":"2021-02-28T07:33:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T05:53:00.000Z","uid":19454,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"8f8c3b913e98e243b636aa24006a2832cbdcef3c","tid":2426582,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T07:33:00.000Z","msg":"中國上海一名 iPhone 用戶日前以蘋果公司濫用市場支配地位涉嫌壟斷為起訴 Apple 公司，要求賠償 10 萬人民幣，目前已經受上海法院受理。<br />\n<br />\n起訴狀顯示，該用戶因為不滿 App Store 的內購相比 Android 平台更貴，其中包括愛奇藝、喜馬拉雅、網易雲音樂等 App 的會員服務，並表示在 iOS 平台購買只能夠通過 App Store 付款，而無法使用第三方付款方式。<br />\n<br />\n實際上通過 App Store 內購，開發者需要付額外 30% 的佣金給蘋果，這也是為什麼 YouTube Premium，iOS 會比 Android 定價更高的原因。<br />\n<br />\nApple 目前並未針對事件作出回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2021/02/27/shanghai-users-are-dissatisfied-that-ios-in-app-purchases/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2021%2F02%2F27%2Fshanghai-users-are-dissatisfied-that-ios-in-app-purchases%2F&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3m58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=82e468b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2021/02/27/shanghai-users-are-dissatisfied-that-ios-in-app-purchases/</a>"},{"pid":"bd2c59553c4966c2fd54e7b26ec1549868547289","tid":2426582,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T07:33:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b593a20d9069826280f5381bd37b24581c8edd6","tid":2426582,"uid":103759,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T07:34:10.000Z","msg":"冇錢就咪用iPhone 啦"},{"pid":"a103a8d15aaaf81296b15ec6ea54355ed6108c34","tid":2426582,"uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"c